  "game": {
    "title": "Fruit Mountain Party – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition Upgrade Pack",
    "description": "The mega-hit 3D puzzle game “Fruit Mountain” — where you merge fruits to make them bigger — is now a party battle game for everyone!\nThis time, it’s a fruit battle!? Jump into versus mode with up to 4 players!\nWith items and wild surprises, it’s a chaotic battle full of laughs!\nKeep stacking those fruits!\n\n[Easy to Play!]\nJust toss fruits onto the plate and stack them up.\nMerge two of the same fruit to create a bigger one!\nThe bigger the fruit you make, the higher your score climbs!\nBe careful not to let fruits fall off the plate — merge them skillfully!\nMaster your stacking technique and take on your rivals!\n\n[Battle Together!]\n・Compete against rivals worldwide online!\nCreate a Room and invite friends to battle anytime, anywhere!\n・Local versus play offline too!\nUp to 4 players can play locally on a single Nintendo Switch 2! Get everyone together for some fun!\n\n[Tons of Game Modes!]\nMultiple versus modes! Try different styles and have a blast!\n・Standard Race\n・Thief Frenzy\n・Fruit of the Sun\n・Great Harvest\n・Survival\n\n[Single Player Too!]\nHone your skills against NPCs and prepare for online battles!\nIn “Time Attack” mode, race to complete a watermelon as fast as you can!\nAim for the fastest time! Climb the rankings!\n\n[Collection]\nCustomize your plate with the dress-up feature! Show off your style with your favorite plate!",
